I don't think so, given that the parameter (`-first`) is declared as a _scalar_.

(If it were declared as an _array_, asking for multiple selections would make more sense, but it would raise questions about the keyboard interface: how would you mark a selection without submitting it at the same time? Currently, each array element must be specified / tab-completed individually.)

